		<hr />
		
		
		
		
		<div>I always like going back through these threads to see what people asked for, what we got and who complained about everything.  This thread has many suggestions that were implemented (Impel, Patient Harvest, Instanukes),  and some that weren't (Disintegrate upgrade, Reverse CoTH). <br />
<br />
What it really had was a lot of good discussion that got us to the spot we are in today, which is KICK ASS.  Yeah, I wish we had MGB TL to &lt;location&gt; and could in place evac while warping mobs back to spawn point.  However, I see how many things we have gotten and play my wizard in happiness. <br />
<br />
Now, if someone could just figure out how to get us Tracking....</div>
